%N A014995 Inverse of 986th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A014995 Periodic with period length 986. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A014995 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A014995/b014995.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%H A014995 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 986.
%H A014995 <a href="/index/Rec#order_448">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 448.
%H A014995 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A014995 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%o A014995 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(986)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
